all your time and
all your money.

00:14:24.330 --> 00:14:25.731 align:middle line:90%
You don't have to do diet pills.

00:14:25.731 --> 00:14:27.700 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to
starve yourself.

00:14:27.700 --> 00:14:31.470 align:middle line:84%
You can eat six times a day,
and you can do it simply.

00:14:31.470 --> 00:14:32.405 align:middle line:90%
Five ingredients.

00:14:32.405 --> 00:14:34.206 align:middle line:84%
And save time at
the grocery store,

00:14:34.206 --> 00:14:35.908 align:middle line:84%
save time in the
kitchen, and save money.

00:14:35.908 --> 00:14:36.842 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Yes.

00:14:36.842 --> 00:14:38.177 align:middle line:84%
So, in the essence
of saving time,

00:14:38.177 --> 00:14:39.946 align:middle line:84%
that's sometimes
all I have time for,

00:14:39.946 --> 00:14:41.514 align:middle line:84%
is just to put a
few things together

00:14:41.514 --> 00:14:44.150 align:middle line:84%
that are identifiable foods,
and then either pack it up,

00:14:44.150 --> 00:14:46.252 align:middle line:84%
walk out, pack it
in a lunch book --

00:14:46.252 --> 00:14:47.687 align:middle line:90%
box, do what I need to do.

00:14:47.687 --> 00:14:50.289 align:middle line:84%
You did all of this
as a single mom, too.

