So, I was, like, I want
to create something;

00:15:16.716 --> 00:15:19.752 align:middle line:84%
I want to create recipes
that -- five ingredients.

00:15:19.752 --> 00:15:21.587 align:middle line:84%
>> LG: So, I want to touch
on that for a second.

