00:38:49.961 --> 00:38:50.495 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Turmeric ...

00:38:50.495 --> 00:38:51.329 align:middle line:90%
>> DM: Yes.

00:38:51.329 --> 00:38:53.264 align:middle line:90%
