00:39:08.946 --> 00:39:10.214 align:middle line:90%
>> DM: You can.

00:39:10.214 --> 00:39:13.684 align:middle line:84%
You can find recipes that
provide turmeric in it --

00:39:13.684 --> 00:39:15.653 align:middle line:84%
I like putting it in
my eggs in the morning

00:39:15.653 --> 00:39:17.889 align:middle line:84%
because it's not
super, super strong.

00:39:17.889 --> 00:39:20.591 align:middle line:84%
I put about a teaspoon in
my eggs, but how I love

00:39:20.591 --> 00:39:22.860 align:middle line:84%
