know I'm getting it --

00:39:22.860 --> 00:39:23.995 align:middle line:90%
I look at it like a concoction.

00:39:23.995 --> 00:39:26.998 align:middle line:84%
So in the morning I used
to just do lemon water.

00:39:26.998 --> 00:39:29.967 align:middle line:84%
Now I do my lemon water, I put
a teaspoon of turmeric in it,

00:39:29.967 --> 00:39:32.103 align:middle line:84%
and I do a pinch of
cayenne in there.

00:39:32.103 --> 00:39:34.305 align:middle line:84%
So then I know -- and if
I need a little sweet,

00:39:34.305 --> 00:39:36.841 align:middle line:84%
usually at night I like to
add a little bit of honey...

00:39:36.841 --> 00:39:37.642 align:middle line:90%
>> LG: Oh, that's interesting.

00:39:37.642 --> 00:39:38.576 align:middle line:90%
