00:40:18.783 --> 00:40:20.952 align:middle line:90%
Take a look.

00:40:20.952 --> 00:40:21.586 align:middle line:90%
>> DM: [Background Music] Hi.

00:40:21.586 --> 00:40:22.553 align:middle line:90%
