led to believe are healthy

00:46:36.160 --> 00:46:39.129 align:middle line:84%
and will help you lose
weight, but I would avoid them.

00:46:39.129 --> 00:46:41.432 align:middle line:84%
The first one is
artificial sweeteners

00:46:41.432 --> 00:46:44.702 align:middle line:84%
