00:46:59.016 --> 00:47:01.752 align:middle line:84%
such as 100 % maple
syrup, stevia, and honey.

00:47:01.752 --> 00:47:08.092 align:middle line:84%
The second thing is 100 %
whole wheat breads and pastas,

00:47:08.092 --> 00:47:10.561 align:middle line:84%
reduced fat whole
wheat crackers --

00:47:10.561 --> 00:47:13.531 align:middle line:84%
these items are going to
spike your blood sugars.

00:47:13.531 --> 00:47:16.567 align:middle line:84%
When you spike your blood
sugars, it converts right

00:47:16.567 --> 00:47:20.371 align:middle line:84%
into fat and the idea of getting
rid of all complex carbs --

00:47:20.371 --> 00:47:22.540 align:middle line:90%
that's not a good idea either.

00:47:22.540 --> 00:47:25.276 align:middle line:84%
Things like slow-cooked
oatmeal, rice,

00:47:25.276 --> 00:47:28.913 align:middle line:84%
